description:
This is a 20 minute workout called 'Gentle Pilates Workout with Guided Breathing | At Home | No equipment | 20 Mins' from the channel The Girl With The Pilates Mat.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Enjoy this 20 minute full body Pilates workout you can do at home, no equipment needed and no impact on the body. We focus on building strength and tone whilst the guided breathing fills the body with oxygen encouraging relaxation as well as enhancing the benefits of the exercises. It'll  leave you feeling both relaxed, de-stressed and ready for whatever you will be doing next in your day.

Please click the Like button, leave me a comment below and Subscribe to the channel to help me make more films just for you. 

Stay safe, stay well and enjoy every moment of this day,
Take care, Rachel  x
